      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its aesthetic perfection. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the individual who demands nothing less than an impeccable automotive profile.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
